title: Ep 14: Humor with Matt Braunger
description: Believe it or not, there is a Philosophy of Humor. It starts with Plato and guess what? He didn't like it very much...why? Because you'll have to listen to find out, silly goose! My guest is Matt Braunger, a very funny human and together we get deep on comedy.
author: nadav@ymhstudios.com (Christina Pazsitzky)
